thread.title: SEE PING
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by SEE PING

author: SEE PING
title: SEE PING
text: Very good service provided by the counter personnel. But the down side is after you got your key, there is no one there to provide you any service , there is a guy who from the booth just point to you the car which you had booked, no inspection was done to the car, before we leave . Any way,luckily we got our car in a good condition and cleaned. With the top dog package which is highly recommended, save all the trouble and you don't need to worry about any things regarding the insurance and is all covered.
